Metallica - 6 Feet Down Under - 2 (Live EP's) 2010-15 320ak

Six Feet Down Under Part II is a limited edition commemorative live EP by the American heavy metal band Metallica. It is the second part of the band's previous live EP, Six Feet Down Under, and was released in Australia and New Zealand only, on November 12, 2010 through Universal Music. 

Like the EP's preceder (part one), it has been sold by Trans-Tasman record stores, Metallica online store and iTunes only, and contains eight songs from the early part of the tour in Australia and New Zealand in 2010 as voted by members of the Metallica Fan Club living in those areas.

Here are both together so enjoy...
